# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.0.2] - Snapshot
  ### Added
  - Added work in progress lisb api doc
  - Added machine-headers refinement, implementation, model and system.
  - Added translation of USES, EXTENDS, INCLUDES, SEES, PROMOTES and operation substitutions.
  - Added parameter support to machine-header and machine-reference.
  - Added to lisb and ir multiple arguments for constraints, properties, invariants and init.
  Arguments for constraints, properties and invariants are chained via AConjunctPredicate.
  Arguments for init are chained via ASequenceSubstitution.
  - Added example sebastian with tests.
  ### Changed
  - Changed lisb and ir invariant to invariants.
  - Changed all machine-clause-ir-nodes to use :values instead of individually keys for arguments.
  - Changed lisb machine layout
  ### Removed
  - Removed lisb and ir call. Only apply is now used for function calls.
  - Removed maplet/couple chaining.
  - Removed b machines for machine-clauses


## [0.0.1] - 2021-09-17
